summary: The document is a restricted military record detailing an investigation into Manuel Marti, a DOD-affiliated personnel, conducted by the INSCOM/CSF. It includes findings from credit agencies in New York, which reported no records for Marti. Marked as unclassified but released with deletions, the document was last reviewed on 03/07/95.
key_findings: The investigation into Manuel Marti was part of broader DOD-affiliated personnel incident investigations.
Credit Bureau of Greater New York found no records for Manuel Marti.
The document, though unclassified, was released with certain deletions and last reviewed on 03/07/95.
